#

Fire-Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Roasted Seasonal Vegetables and Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$25.99
800 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

ChickenGrilledComfort FoodSeasonal

Description

A succulent chicken dish marinated in zesty lemon and fresh herbs, served alongside vibrant seasonal vegetables and creamy garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Chicken Breast: 4 pieces
  • Fresh Lemon Juice: 1/4 cup
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Garlic Cloves, minced: 4
  • Fresh Herbs (Thyme, Rosemary): 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Assorted Seasonal Vegetables (Zucchini, Bell Peppers, Carrots): 4 cups
  • Butter (for mashed potatoes): 1/2 cup
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Potatoes, peeled and quartered: 2 pounds
